        <p class="hint-textarea" id="cr-words-hint">Examples: &quot;enrolled bill signed&quot;, &quot;leak detection dog&quot;</p>
        <textarea aria-describedby="cr-words-hint" class="expand80-2000 words-and-phrases" name="wordsPhrases" id="congressional-record-wordsPhrases"></textarea>
