"></a><a name="_Toc197439347"></a><a name="_Toc205888905"></a><a name="_Toc205889058"></a><a name="_Toc205992243"></a><a name="_Toc207195785"></a>Figure 1. Terrestrial-Based Detection of Ballistic Missiles vs. Hypersonic Glide Vehicles</p>
