<p class="TableTitle"><a name="_Ref34662285"></a><a name="_Toc34660938"></a><a name="_Toc34662261"></a><a name="_Toc34662413"></a><a name="_Toc34744047"></a><a name="_Toc35330647"></a><a name="_Toc49427039"></a><a name="_Toc55549531"></a><a name="_Toc55549574"></a><a name="_Toc55571480"></a><a name="_Toc57101224"></a><a name="_Toc57728527"></a><a name="_Toc57819327"></a><a name="_Toc57968431"></a><a name="_Toc57968706"></a><a name="_Toc70340093"></a><a name="_Toc70603241"></a><a name="_Toc70603458"></a><a name="_Toc76969801"></a><a name="_Toc85531991"></a><a name="_Toc98424152"></a><a name="_Toc98429418"></a><a name="_Toc98771279"></a><a name="_Toc98771514"></a><a name="_Toc102655605"></a><a name="_Toc102656642"></a><a name="_Toc109210418"></a><a name="_Toc116628496"></a><a name="_Toc116915743"></a><a name="_Toc116915871"></a><a name="_Toc117780067"></a><a name="_Toc117837250"></a><a name="_Toc121839441"></a><a name="_Toc121840428"></a><a name="_Toc122008964"></a><a name="_Toc124249311"></a><a name="_Toc124347458"></a><a name="_Toc127193059"></a><a name="_Toc127275553"></a><a name="_Toc127275598"></a><a name="_Toc158213136"></a><a name="_Toc158379857"></a><a name="_Toc158379987"></a><a name="_Toc158380342"></a><a name="_Toc158714515"></a><a name="_Toc158715057"></a><a name="_Toc158716105"></a><a name="_Toc173922457"></a><a name="_Toc173923852"></a><a name="_Toc173923995"></a><a name="_Toc174022966"></a><a name="_Toc174545705"></a><a name="_Toc184035641"></a><a name="_Toc184139471"></a><a name="_Toc186710321"></a><a name="_Toc186712002"></a><a name="_Toc187068037"></a><a name="_Toc189062292"></a><a name="_Toc189236800"></a><a name="_Toc190174463"></a><a name="_Toc195197090"></a><a name="_Toc197352880"></a><a name="_Toc197354317"></a><a name="_Toc197439350"></a><a name="_Toc205888908"></a><a name="_Toc205889061"></a><a name="_Toc205992246"></a><a name="_Toc207195788"></a>Table 1. Summary of Selected U.S. Hypersonic Weapons RDT&amp;E Funding</p>
</div>
