<p class="TableSource"><strong>Source:</strong> Program information taken from U.S. Army and Air Force FY2025 and FY2026 Justification Books, available at <a class="ExternalLink" href="https://comptroller.defense.gov/Budget-Materials/" target="_blank"><span class="Hyperlink">https://comptroller.defense.gov/</span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink">Budget-Materials/</span></a><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span>.</p>
