</p><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="FigureBox" width="5">
<tr>
<td>
<p class="FigureTitle"><a name="_Ref13737934"></a><a name="_Toc12540250"></a><a name="_Toc12541733"></a><a name="_Toc13582709"></a><a name="_Toc13654302"></a><a name="_Toc13745071"></a><a name="_Toc13817377"></a><a name="_Toc19627126"></a><a name="_Toc19628946"></a><a name="_Toc34225128"></a><a name="_Toc34660937"></a><a name="_Toc34662260"></a><a name="_Toc34662412"></a><a name="_Toc34744046"></a><a name="_Toc35330646"></a><a name="_Toc49427038"></a><a name="_Toc55549530"></a><a name="_Toc55549573"></a><a name="_Toc55571479"></a><a name="_Toc57101223"></a><a name="_Toc57728526"></a><a name="_Toc57819326"></a><a name="_Toc57968430"></a><a name="_Toc57968705"></a><a name="_Toc70340092"></a><a name="_Toc70603240"></a><a name="_Toc70603457"></a><a name="_Toc76969800"></a><a name="_Toc85531990"></a><a name="_Toc98424151"></a><a name="_Toc98429417"></a><a name="_Toc98771278"></a><a name="_Toc98771513"></a><a name="_Toc102655604"></a><a name="_Toc102656641"></a><a name="_Toc109210417"></a><a name="_Toc116628495"></a><a name="_Toc116915742"></a><a name="_Toc116915870"></a><a name="_Toc117780066"></a><a name="_Toc117837249"></a><a name="_Toc121839440"></a><a name="_Toc121840427"></a><a name="_Toc122008963"></a><a name="_Toc124249310"></a><a name="_Toc124347457"></a><a name="_Toc127193058"></a><a name="_Toc127275552"></a><a name="_Toc127275597"></a><a name="_Toc158213135"></a><a name="_Toc158379856"></a><a name="_Toc158379986"></a><a name="_Toc158380341"></a><a name="_Toc158714514"></a><a name="_Toc158715056"></a><a name="_Toc158716104"></a><a name="_Toc173922456"></a><a name="_Toc173923851"></a><a name="_Toc173923994"></a><a name="_Toc174022965"></a><a name="_Toc174545704"></a><a name="_Toc184035640"></a><a name="_Toc184139470"></a><a name="_Toc186710320"></a><a name="_Toc186712001"></a><a name="_Toc187068036"></a><a name="_Toc189062291"></a><a name="_Toc189236799"></a><a name="_Toc190174462"></a><a name="_Toc195197089"></a><a name="_Toc197352879"></a><a name="_Toc197354316"></a><a name="_Toc197439349"></a><a name="_Toc205888907"></a><a name="_Toc205889060"></a><a name="_Toc205992245"></a><a name="_Toc207195787"></a>Figure 3. Lingyun-1 Hypersonic Cruise Missile Prototype </p>
