<p class="FootnoteText"> Mikayla Easley, "Grady: DOD preparing for 'hypersonics 2.0 and 3.0' to understand operational concepts," <em>Defense Scoop</em>, November 22, 2024, at <a class="ExternalLink" href="https://defensescoop.com/2024/11/22/dod-grady-hypersonics-2-0-weapons-development-operational-concepts/" target="_blank"><span class="Hyperlink">https://defensescoop.com/2024/11/22/dod-grady-hypersonics-2-0-weapons-development-operational-concepts/</span></a><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span>. </p>
