            </td>
<td>
<p class="FootnoteText"> Sydney J. Freedberg Jr., "Hypersonics: DoD Wants 'Hundreds of Weapons' ASAP," <em>Breaking Defense</em>, April 24, 2020, at <a class="ExternalLink" href="https://breakingdefense.com/2020/04/hypersonics-dod-wants-hundreds-of-weapons-asap/" target="_blank"><span class="Hyperlink">https://breakingdefense.com/2020/04/hypersonics-dod-wants-hundreds-of-weapons-asap/</span></a><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span>.</p>
