</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"><a class="FootnoteBL" href="#ifn151" name="fn151">151</a>.
            </td>
<td>
<p class="FootnoteText"> "Hypersonic Strike and Defense: A Conversation with Mike White," Center for Strategic and International Studies, June 10, 2021, at <a class="ExternalLink" href="https://www.csis.org/analysis/hypersonic-strike-and-defense-conversation-mike-white" target="_blank"><span class="Hyperlink">https://www.csis.org/analysis/hypersonic-strike-and-defense-conversation-mike-white</span></a>. See also Jon Harper, "Just in: Pentagon to Spend Billions Mass-Producing Hypersonic Weapons," <em>National Defens</em><em>e Magazin</em><em>e</em>, March 4, 2020, at <a class="ExternalLink" href="https://www.nationaldefensemagazine.org/articles/2020/3/4/pentagon-to-spend-billions-mass-producing-hypersonic-weapons" target="_blank"><span class="Hyperlink">https://www.nationaldefensemagazine.org/articles/2020/3/4/pentagon-to-spend-billions-mass-producing-hypersonic-weapons</span></a>.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
