            </td>
<td>
<p class="FootnoteText"> Congressional Budget Office, <em>U.S. Hypersonic Weapons and Alternatives</em>, January 2023, at <a class="ExternalLink" href="https://www.cbo.gov/publication/58255" target="_blank"><span class="Hyperlink">https://www.cbo.gov/publication/58255</span></a>.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"><a class="FootnoteBL" href="#ifn153" name="fn153">153</a>.
