<tr>
<td valign="top"><a class="FootnoteBL" href="#ifn155" name="fn155">155</a>.
            </td>
<td>
<p class="FootnoteText"> Aaron Mehta, "Is the Pentagon Moving Quickly Enough on Hypersonic Defense?" <em>Defense News</em>, March 21, 2019, at <a class="ExternalLink" href="https://www.defensenews.com/pentagon/2019/03/21/is-the-pentagon-moving-quickly-enough-on-hypersonic-defense/" target="_blank"><span class="Hyperlink">https://www.defensenews.com/pentagon/2019/03/21/is-the-pentagon-moving-quickly-enough-on-hypersonic-defense/</span></a><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span>.</p>
