<p class="FootnoteText"> CRS Report R41219, <a class="ExternalLink" href="/crs-product/R41219"><em><span class="Hyperlink">The New START Treaty: Central Limits and Key Provisions</span></em></a>, by Amy F. Woolf. </p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
