            </td>
<td>
<p class="FootnoteText"> Mark Gubrud, "Test Ban for Hypersonic Missiles?" Bulletin of the Atomic Scientists, August 6, 2015, at <a class="ExternalLink" href="https://thebulletin.org/roundtable/test-ban-for-hypersonic-missiles/" target="_blank"><span class="Hyperlink">https://thebulletin.org/roundtable/test-ban-for-hypersonic-missiles/</span></a><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span><span class="Hyperlink"></span>.</p>
</td>
</tr>
